title: Amal Clooney Attends the César Awards With George Clooney and Outshines Him on the Red Carpet
text: Amal Clooney Attends the César Awards With George Clooney and Outshines Him on the Red Carpet Most Popular By Alyssa Bailey Feb 24, 2017 Amal Clooney, powerhouse human rights lawyer currently expecting twins, accompanied her actor husband George today at the César Film Awards Ceremony in Paris. They're essentially the French version of the Oscars, and George will be honored . Getty Advertisement - Continue Reading Below Amal came dressed like the Old Hollywood version of Swan Lake 's Odette in a custom-made Atelier Versace gown—and she looked stunning: Getty She sets set the bar high for maternity fashion this weekend . Stylists preparing for Sunday's Academy Awards ceremony, take note. More from ELLE:
